<div class="main">
    <h1>Naive Bayes Text Analyzer</h1>
  <p>
    Your text input is processed against a lexicon containing positive and
    negative opinion words and 'Rotten Tomatoes' movie reviews,
    the Text Analyzer will classify your input text as either
    positive or negative.
  </p>

  <h3>Enter text to analyze</h3>
  <form method="post" action="/result">
    <div>
      <textarea name="text_to_analyze" rows='11' cols='75'><%= @previous_input %></textarea>
    </div>
    <div>
      <input type="submit" value="Analyze">
    </div>
  </form>
</div>

